survey_response.review_text: I visited today this clinic and met Dr. Joshna Mohan jyotsana mohan . She is the best doctor that I have experienced. While treatment I had no pain while she was injecting. Easily had the RCT and quick treatment. She is very polite and charged minimal amount in metro city like Delhi. I recommend this is a best place for the dental health and treatment.

I came to know about this clinic from one of my friend and to my surprise the clinic is very hi tech , well maintained , patient care and patient hygiene is the top priority over here. The complete staff of Dr. Vijays Dental Spa is very friendly, and the dentists are very good in explaining all the possible treatments that can be done . My ortho case is very well taken care of by Dr. Vijay. * **** *** ** ** *** **** ************ ** *** *****

I just recently had my braces taken off nd to my amazement,underneath was the most beautiful smile i ever could have dreamed possible.The entire procedure was painless and my most relaxed dental experience ever,thanks to the comprehensive care and support of this wonderful team after my experience.I just wanted to thank you to staff of dental spa team and i would highly recommend Dr. Vijay and the entire dental spa team.

I would definitely recommend Dr. vijay  for all your dental needs. All the best
